### Add a new item
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My First Item",
  "description": "This is my first item created via REST Client"
}

### Get all items
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/items

### Add another item (only name required)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Simple Item"
}

### Get specific item (replace 1 with actual ID)
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/items/1
